cast.overview: A woman is released from prison after serving a sentence for a violent crime and re-enters a society that refuses to forgive her past.
cast.title: The Unforgivable

details.biography: Jess McLeod is an actor hailing from Vancouver, British Columbia, and has been acting professionally since childhood. They have won two Leo Awards, and been nominated for the Rising Star award at WorldFest Houston. Upcoming projects include a series regular role in both seasons of Peacock's series One of Us is Lying, based on the NYT bestseller of the same name, and a supporting role in Netflix's Untitled Sandra Bullock/Nora Fingscheidt Project.
details.name: Jess McLeod
